      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Many damais rely on their incredible force of personality and in-the-moment ingenuity to get themselves out of scrapes, rather than on the survival skills common among their fellows. Damais with this species trait gain a +2 species bonus to Bluff and Sense Motive checks. In addition, when they aid another creature using one of these skills, the aid another bonus they provide increases to +3.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces survivor.</strong></p>"
